<br />one more thing...
<br />
<br />In writing OAM, you write at OAMADDR once then you write at OAMDATA. In reading OAM, you write at OAMADDR once then you read at OAMDATA or OAM_DMA. Write increments the OAMADDR, read on vblank is not incremented. Was that all??? or am I missing something??? does OAM reside at PPU address $0000-$00FF????  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" />

		

